Chatsworth police are appealing to the members of the community to assist with regards to a murder case that they are investigating. Chatsworth SAPS communications, Captain Cheryl Pillay said on 3 June 2018, at approximately 9am, the body of the a woman was found at the Lusaka Informal Settlement in Moorton, Chatsworth, with multiple stab wounds.<br />
